import { Box,Typography } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'
// import photo1 from '../../../Photos/photo1.webp'
import Rough from './Rough'

function Product() {
  return (
    <Box style={{'display':'flex','justifyContent':'center'}}>
        <Box>
        <Typography
            variant="p"
            noWrap
            component="p"
          >
           Apple Product
          </Typography>
          <Typography
            variant="p"
            // noWrap
            component="p"
            sx={{fontSize:"25px"}}
          >
           New Apple AirPods (3D Generation)
          </Typography>
          <Typography
            variant="p"
            // noWrap
            component="p"
          >
           It's magic, remasterd!
          </Typography>
          <Typography
            variant="p"
            // noWrap
            component="ul"
          >
          <Typography
            variant="p"
            // noWrap
            component="li"
          >
           Spatial audio with dynamic head tracking places sound all around you
          </Typography>
          <Typography
            variant="p"
            // noWrap
            component="li"
          >
            Adaptive EQ automatically tunes music to your ears
          </Typography>
          <Typography
            variant="p"
            // noWrap
            component="li"
          >
            All-new contoured design
          </Typography>
          </Typography>
        </Box>

        <Box>
            <Rough/>
        </Box>
    </Box>
  )
}

export default Product
